definition: tool/device/utensil/equipment/instrument/talent/ability/to possess/to have/to provide/to furnish/to state/classifier for devices, coffins, dead bodies

sentences.english: Patterns are part of the software professional's toolbox today.
sentences.chinese: 模式是当今软件专业人员工具箱中的一部分。

sentences.english: The worker felt for a few screws in a tool box .
sentences.chinese: 这位工人在工具箱里摸来摸去找几个螺丝钉。

sentences.english: Nick leaned back against my toolbox.
sentences.chinese: 尼克靠在了我的工具箱上。

sentences.english: The stockroom used kits from bins that incoming inspection filled.
sentences.chinese: 仓库使用工具箱引入检查。

sentences.english: Select the Ellipse Tool from the Toolbox.
sentences.chinese: 从工具箱中选择椭圆工具。

sentences.english: The toolkit will report that it is scanning the project.
sentences.chinese: 工具箱将会报告说它正在扫描这个项目。

sentences.english: I hope your parents had all the right tools in their toolbox.
sentences.chinese: 我希望你的父母拥有所有工具箱里正确的工具。

sentences.english: This was in the plane's toolbox. There's only one flare.
sentences.chinese: 这是飞机工具箱里的，只有一个照明弹。

sentences.english: This is not quite what I want, as I don't have a starting toolbox.
sentences.chinese: 这是不大我想要的，因为我没有启动工具箱。

sentences.english: But what about using toolboxes for your crafting?
sentences.chinese: 但是如果是用工具箱来盛放手工艺品呢？

sentences.english: EMERGENCY】I keep a box of tools and a fire extinguisher in my car for use in an emergency.
sentences.chinese: 我在车中放了工具箱和灭火器，以备紧急之需。

sentences.english: The micro-controller is like any other element of the kit.
sentences.chinese: 微控制器就好像工具箱中其他的部件。

sentences.english: Normally, you choose one of these toolkits or the other.
sentences.chinese: 通常来讲，您需要从这两种工具箱中选择其中之一。

sentences.english: The UNA toolbox can be downloaded here.
sentences.chinese: UNA工具箱可以在这里下载。

sentences.english: Permanently attached metal nameplate listing kit number and all components.
sentences.chinese: 所有附件和工具箱上都有永久性金属标示牌。

sentences.english: Install the Topology Domain Generation Toolkit.
sentences.chinese: 安装拓扑域生成工具箱。
